'''加拿大改革黨'''（{{lang-en|Reform Party of Canada}}；{{lang-fr|Parti réformiste du Canada}}）是一個[[右派民粹主義|右派民粹主義]]<ref name="RemillardGuides2003">{{cite book|author1=Francois Remillard|author2=Ulysses Travel Guides|title=Quebec|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=AIPrKia8zaAC&pg=PA22|date=2003-04-01|publisher=Ulysses Travel Guides|isbn=978-2-89464-595-6|pages=22–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144036/http://books.google.com/books?id=AIPrKia8zaAC&pg=PA22|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Abedi2004">{{cite book|author=Amir Abedi|title=Anti-Political Establishment Parties: A Comparative Analysis|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Skx-AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA39|date=2004-07-31|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-134-36369-8|pages=39–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144251/http://books.google.com/books?id=Skx-AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA39|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Bauman/Kahana">{{cite book|author=Bauman/Kahana|title=The Least Examined Branch: The Role of Legislatures in the Constitutional State|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=0KpYkm9SJvAC&pg=PA161|publisher=Cambridge University Press|isbn=978-1-139-46040-8|pages=161–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144103/http://books.google.com/books?id=0KpYkm9SJvAC&pg=PA161|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Young2000">{{cite book|author=Lisa Young|title=Feminists and Party Politics|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=6glKtBtpdkQC&pg=PA133|year=2000|publisher=UBC Press|isbn=978-0-7748-0774-6|pages=133–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144029/http://books.google.com/books?id=6glKtBtpdkQC&pg=PA133|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="LoughlinKincaid">{{cite book|author1=John Loughlin|author2=John Kincaid|author3=Wilfried Swenden|title=Routledge Handbook of Regionalism & Federalism|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=R5F6MjBW1G8C&pg=RA5-PT29|date=2013-07-18|publisher=Routledge|isbn=1-136-72769-8|pages=5–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144011/http://books.google.com/books?id=R5F6MjBW1G8C&pg=RA5-PT29|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DornanPammett2001">{{cite book|author1=Christopher Dornan|author2=Jon H. Pammett|title=The Canadian General Election of 2000|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Tpjvv0ND2PkC&pg=PA133|date=2001-05-01|publisher=Dundurn|isbn=978-1-55488-015-7|pages=133–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144035/http://books.google.com/books?id=Tpjvv0ND2PkC&pg=PA133|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="DrachePerin1992">{{cite book|author1=Daniel Drache|author2=Roberto Perin|title=Negotiating with a Sovereign Quebec|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=lMiirZfKpXwC&pg=PA77|date=1992-01-01|publisher=James Lorimer & Company|isbn=978-1-55028-392-1|pages=77–|access-date=2014-06-18|archive-date=2014-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140704144113/http://books.google.com/books?id=lMiirZfKpXwC&pg=PA77|dead-url=no}}</ref>政黨，存在於1987年至2000年。該黨於2000年由[[加拿大聯盟|加拿大聯盟]]繼承，加拿大聯盟在2003年與[[加拿大進步保守黨|進步保守黨]]合併形成[[加拿大保守黨|加拿大保守黨]]。

